{"title":"初学 HTML 笔记","uid":"8b6fa26fae20036bf07fb3b7eac5e80f","slug":"LearnHTML","date":"2024-09-24T04:56:53.000Z","updated":"2024-10-28T06:51:53.120Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/LearnHTML.json","keywords":"HerikoDeltana,HRiver2,","cover":"https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/66f2473ef21886ccc08288cc.png","content":"<p>「什么是 HTML 啊我请问了？」</p>\r\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\r\n<!-- toc -->\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>跟随 <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/\">MDN WEB DOCS</a>\r\n学习</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<h2 id=\"基础\">01 基础</h2>\r\n<p>主体上跟随 MDN 学习，所以内容会是接近的，现在这一部分对应着 <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Learn/Getting_started_with_the_web/HTML_basics\">HTML\r\n基础</a>。</p>\r\n<p>当然还有非常易懂的学长的 PPT.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"一张网页基本元素结构\">一张网页基本元素&amp;结构</h3>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&lt;!DOCTYPE <span class=\"keyword\">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">html</span> <span class=\"attr\">lang</span> = <span class=\"string\">\"zh-CN\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">meta</span> <span class=\"attr\">charset</span> = <span class=\"string\">\"utf-8\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">meta</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span> = <span class=\"string\">\"viewport\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">content</span> = <span class=\"string\">\"width=device-width\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">title</span>&gt;</span>Title<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">title</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><code>&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</code>\r\n文档类型，告诉浏览器如何解析网页，保证文档的正常读取。</li>\r\n<li><code>&lt;html&gt;</code> 这个元素是网页的顶层容器，唯一的根元素。\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><code>lang</code> 属性表示网页内容的默认语言，比如\r\n<code>zh-CN</code>、<code>en-US</code> 等。</li>\r\n</ul></li>\r\n<li><code>&lt;head&gt;</code>\r\n元素是一个容器元素，用于放置网站的元信息，其中内容一般不会出现在用户可见的网页上。\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><code>&lt;meta charset = \"utf-8\"/&gt;</code> 该元素指明你的文档使用\r\nUTF-8\r\n字符编码，以它为编码可以避免以后的某些问题，你的网页不会因为未被识别而被显示为乱码。</li>\r\n<li><code>&lt;meta name = \"viewport\" content = \"width=device-width\"/&gt;</code>\r\n视口元素可以确保页面以视口宽度进行渲染，避免移动端浏览器上因页面过宽导致缩放，利好多端用户的浏览。</li>\r\n<li><code>&lt;title&gt;</code>\r\n元素用于指定网页的标题，其中设置的内容会出现在浏览器的标题栏。</li>\r\n</ul></li>\r\n<li><code>&lt;body&gt;</code> 元素则是希望用户看见的内容。</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 id=\"语义结构\">语义结构</h4>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">header</span>&gt;</span>页眉<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">header</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">nav</span>&gt;</span>导航栏<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">nav</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">main</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">aside</span>&gt;</span>侧边栏<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">aside</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">article</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">h1</span>&gt;</span>文章标题<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">h2</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">article</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">section</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">section</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">main</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">footer</span>&gt;</span>页尾<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">footer</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n<h4 id=\"通用属性\">通用属性</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><code>id</code> 属性指定元素额外标识符</li>\r\n<li><code>class</code> 属性对网页元素进行分类</li>\r\n<li><code>style</code> 属性用来指定当前元素样式（CSS）</li>\r\n<li><code>data-*</code> 属性存放自定义数据</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>比如：</p>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">ol</span> <span class=\"attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"list\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span> <span class=\"attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"list-item\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">id</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"list-item-1\"</span>&gt;</span> item 1 <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span> <span class=\"attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"list-item list-item-active\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">style</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"color: blue\"</span>&gt;</span> item 2 <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span> <span class=\"attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"list-item\"</span>&gt;</span> item 3 <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">ol</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n<ol class=\"list\">\r\n<li class=\"list-item\" id=\"list-item-1\">\r\nitem 1\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-item list-item-active\" style=\"color: blue\">\r\nitem 2\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-item\">\r\nitem 3\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h4 id=\"块级元素和行内元素\">块级元素和行内元素</h4>\r\n<p>元素分为两大块：block 块级元素和 inline 行内元素。</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>block：默认占据一个独立的区域，在网页上会自动另起一行，占据 100%\r\n的宽度。</li>\r\n<li>inline：默认与其他元素在同一行，不会产生换行。</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id=\"html-元素\">HTML 元素</h3>\r\n<p>以这一句为例：</p>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">p</span> <span class=\"attr\">class</span> = <span class=\"string\">\"editor-note\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">id</span> = <span class=\"string\">\"paragraph-fox\"</span>&gt;</span>The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog.<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n<ol type=\"1\">\r\n<li><code>&lt;p class = \"editor-note\" id = \"paragraph-fox\"&gt;</code>：开始标签。\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><code>p</code>：标签/元素名称。</li>\r\n<li><code>class = \"editor-note\"</code>：元素的一个属性，形式为\r\n<code>key = \"value\"</code>，<code>id = \"paragraph-fox\"</code>\r\n同理。</li>\r\n</ul></li>\r\n<li><code>The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog.</code>：内容。</li>\r\n<li><code>&lt;/p&gt;</code>：结束标签。</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h4 id=\"嵌套\">嵌套</h4>\r\n<p>元素也可以嵌套，比如：</p>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span> My cat is <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">strong</span>&gt;</span>very<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">strong</span>&gt;</span> grumpy.<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n<p>\r\nMy cat is <strong>very</strong> grumpy.\r\n</p>\r\n<h4 id=\"注释\">注释</h4>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">&lt;!--</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">hide and seek</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">--&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n<h4 id=\"图像\">图像</h4>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">img</span> <span class=\"attr\">src</span> = <span class=\"string\">\"https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/66f2473ef21886ccc08288cc.png\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">alt</span> = <span class=\"string\">\"Where is my image???\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/66f2473ef21886ccc08288cc.png\" alt=\"Where is my image???\"></p>\r\n<p><code>src</code> 后面跟着图片的地址，<code>alt</code>\r\n后面跟着图片描述。</p>\r\n<h4 id=\"标题\">标题</h4>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">h1</span>&gt;</span>一级标题<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">h1</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">h2</span>&gt;</span>二级标题<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">h2</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n<p>以此类推，一直到 <code>&lt;h6&gt;</code></p>\r\n<h4 id=\"列表\">列表</h4>\r\n<p>分为有序列表和无序列表，分别为 <code>&lt;ol&gt;</code> 和\r\n<code>&lt;ul&gt;</code>，使用例：</p>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span>Good Morning! there is something only Apple can do:<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">strong</span>&gt;</span>60Hz<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">strong</span>&gt;</span> Screen On iPhone 16<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span>Slower charging speed on Apple Watch S10<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span>Only <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">strong</span>&gt;</span>27W<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">strong</span>&gt;</span> on iPhone 16<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span>iPhone 16 start with <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">strong</span>&gt;</span>128GB<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">strong</span>&gt;</span> SKU<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">strong</span>&gt;</span>Only Apple Can Do!<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">strong</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span>Good Morning, there is something only Google can deliver:<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">ol</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span>Tensor G4, just like Kirin 9010, how?<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">ol</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">strong</span>&gt;</span>Only Google Can Deliver!<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">strong</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n<p>\r\nGood Morning! there is something only Apple can do:\r\n</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<strong>60Hz</strong> Screen On iPhone 16\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\nSlower charging speed on Apple Watch S10\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\nOnly <strong>27W</strong> on iPhone 16\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\niPhone 16 start with only <strong>128GB</strong> SKU\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n<strong>Only Apple Can Do!</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nGood Morning, there is something only Google can deliver:\r\n</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>\r\nTensor G4's performance level just like <b>Sanctioned Kirin 9010</b>.\r\nhow? why?\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n<strong>Only Google Can Deliver!</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<h4 id=\"链接\">链接</h4>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">a</span> <span class=\"attr\">href</span> = <span class=\"string\">\"https://hriver2.github.io/\"</span>&gt;</span>Heriko Deltana's Blog<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">a</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://hriver2.github.io/\">Heriko Deltana's Blog</a></p>\r\n<p>而 <code>target</code>\r\n属性可以指定在哪里打开链接，比如，<code>target = \"_blank\"</code>\r\n即为在新标签页打开。</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><code>_self</code> 当前页面加载。（默认）</li>\r\n<li><code>_blank</code>\r\n通常在新标签页打开，但用户可以通过配置选择在新窗口打开。</li>\r\n<li><code>_parent</code>\r\n当前浏览环境的父级浏览上下文。如果没有父级框架，行为与\r\n<code>_self</code> 相同。</li>\r\n<li><code>_top</code>\r\n最顶级的浏览上下文（当前浏览上下文中最“高”的祖先）。如果没有祖先，行为与\r\n<code>_self</code> 相同。</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 id=\"表格\">表格</h4>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">table</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">thead</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">th</span>&gt;</span>1<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">th</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">th</span>&gt;</span>2<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">th</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">th</span>&gt;</span>3<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">th</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">th</span>&gt;</span>4<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">th</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">th</span>&gt;</span>5<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">th</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">thead</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">tbody</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">th</span>&gt;</span>Why?<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">th</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span>Only<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span>Apple<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span>Can<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span>Do<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">tbody</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">th</span>&gt;</span>Why not?<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">th</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span>Only<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span>Google<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span>Can<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span>Deliver<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">table</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n<table>\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>\r\n1\r\n</th>\r\n<th>\r\n2\r\n</th>\r\n<th>\r\n3\r\n</th>\r\n<th>\r\n4\r\n</th>\r\n<th>\r\n5\r\n</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>\r\nWhy?\r\n</th>\r\n<td>\r\nOnly\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\nApple\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\nCan\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\nDo\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>\r\nWhy not?\r\n</th>\r\n<td>\r\nOnly\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\nGoogle\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\nCan\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\nDeliver\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</table>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><code>&lt;table&gt;</code> 是一个块级容器元素，表格的容器。</li>\r\n<li><code>&lt;caption&gt;</code> 总是 <code>&lt;table&gt;</code>\r\n里面的第一个子元素，表示表格的标题，但是非必须（比如上面的例子里面就没有）。</li>\r\n<li><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code> 元素表示表格的一行</li>\r\n<li><code>&lt;th&gt;</code> 和 <code>&lt;td&gt;</code>\r\n用于定义表格的单元格。前者是标题单元格，后者是数据单元格。</li>\r\n<li><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> 元素定义了一组定义表格的列头的行。</li>\r\n<li><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code>\r\n元素封装了一系列表格的行（<code>&lt;tr&gt;</code>\r\n元素），代表了它们是表格（<code>&lt;table&gt;</code>）主要内容的组成部分。</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>通常 HTML 表格需要 CSS 进行修饰，比如：</p>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">table</span> {</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">border-collapse</span>: collapse;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">background-color</span>: lightblue;</span><br><span class=\"line\">}</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">td</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">th</span> {</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">border</span>: <span class=\"number\">1px</span> solid black;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">padding</span>: <span class=\"number\">10px</span> <span class=\"number\">20px</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n<style>\r\n  table {\r\n    border-collapse: collapse;\r\n    background-color: lightblue;\r\n  }\r\n  td,\r\n  th {\r\n    border: 1px solid black;\r\n    padding: 10px 20px;\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n<table>\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>\r\n1\r\n</th>\r\n<th>\r\n2\r\n</th>\r\n<th>\r\n3\r\n</th>\r\n<th>\r\n4\r\n</th>\r\n<th>\r\n5\r\n</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>\r\nWhy?\r\n</th>\r\n<td>\r\nOnly\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\nApple\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\nCan\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\nDo\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>\r\nWhy not?\r\n</th>\r\n<td>\r\nOnly\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\nGoogle\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\nCan\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\nDeliver\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</table>\r\n<h4 id=\"表单\">表单</h4>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&lt;!DOCTYPE <span class=\"keyword\">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">html</span> <span class=\"attr\">lang</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"en-US\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">meta</span> <span class=\"attr\">charset</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"utf-8\"</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">title</span>&gt;</span>My first HTML form<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">title</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">form</span> <span class=\"attr\">action</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"/my-handling-form-page\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">method</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"post\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"FORMx\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">label</span> <span class=\"attr\">for</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"name\"</span>&gt;</span>Name:<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">label</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"text\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">id</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"name\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"user_name\"</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">label</span> <span class=\"attr\">for</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"mail\"</span>&gt;</span>E-mail:<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">label</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"email\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">id</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"mail\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"user_mail\"</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">label</span> <span class=\"attr\">for</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"msg\"</span>&gt;</span>Message:<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">label</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">textarea</span> <span class=\"attr\">id</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"msg\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"user_message\"</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">textarea</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span> <span class=\"attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"button\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">button</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"submit\"</span>&gt;</span>Send your message<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">button</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">form</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n<html lang=\"en-US\">\r\n<head>\r\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\r\n<title>\r\nMy first HTML form\r\n</title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<form action=\"/my-handling-form-page\" method=\"post\" name=\"FORMx\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<label for=\"name\">Name:</label>\r\n<input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"user_name\">\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<label for=\"mail\">E-mail:</label>\r\n<input type=\"email\" id=\"mail\" name=\"user_mail\">\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<label for=\"msg\">Message:</label>\r\n<textarea id=\"msg\" name=\"user_message\"></textarea>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"button\">\r\n<button type=\"submit\">\r\nSend your message\r\n</button>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</form>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><code>&lt;form&gt;</code> 容器元素，用于定义一个表单\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><code>action</code> 属性用于指定服务器接受数据的 URL</li>\r\n<li><code>name</code> 属性指定表单的名称，唯一非必须</li>\r\n<li><code>target</code> 在哪个窗口展示数据</li>\r\n<li><code>method</code> 提交数据的 HTTP 方法，一般是 <code>\"get\"</code>\r\n或 <code>\"post\"</code></li>\r\n</ul></li>\r\n<li><code>&lt;label&gt;</code> 行内元素，提供表单控件的文字说明\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><code>for</code> 属性指定关联控件的 <code>id</code> 属性</li>\r\n</ul></li>\r\n<li><code>&lt;button&gt;</code>\r\n标签会生成一个可以点击的按钮，没有默认行为\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><code>type</code> 属性：<code>\"submit\"</code>，<code>\"reset\"</code>\r\n和 <code>\"button\"</code></li>\r\n</ul></li>\r\n<li><code>&lt;select&gt;</code> 下拉菜单\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><code>multiple</code> 属性用于指定是否允许多选</li>\r\n</ul></li>\r\n<li><code>&lt;option&gt;</code> 元素为可以用于\r\n<code>&lt;select&gt;</code> 的选项\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><code>value</code> 属性用于指定值</li>\r\n<li><code>selected</code> 属性用于指定是否为默认选中</li>\r\n</ul></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 id=\"其他\">其他</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><code>&lt;br/&gt;</code> 换行</li>\r\n<li><code>&lt;hr&gt;</code> 水平线</li>\r\n<li><code>&lt;video&gt;</code> 视频</li>\r\n<li><code>&lt;audio&gt;</code> 音频</li>\r\n<li><code>&lt;embed&gt;</code> 用于嵌入外部内容</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n","text":"「什么是 HTML 啊我请问了？」 ...","permalink":"/post/LearnHTML","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"7.1k","symbolsTime":"6 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Web","slug":"Web","count":1,"path":"api/categories/Web.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"HTML","slug":"HTML","count":1,"path":"api/tags/HTML.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80\"><span class=\"toc-text\">01 基础</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%80%E5%BC%A0%E7%BD%91%E9%A1%B5%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84\"><span class=\"toc-text\">一张网页基本元素&amp;结构</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%AF%AD%E4%B9%89%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84\"><span class=\"toc-text\">语义结构</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A8%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7\"><span class=\"toc-text\">通用属性</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%9D%97%E7%BA%A7%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%E5%92%8C%E8%A1%8C%E5%86%85%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">块级元素和行内元素</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#html-%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">HTML 元素</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%B5%8C%E5%A5%97\"><span class=\"toc-text\">嵌套</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%B3%A8%E9%87%8A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">注释</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F\"><sp